# Claude Context Management Vault

**Your visual dashboard for managing Claude Code context quality**

---

## What This Is

This Obsidian vault provides a **graphical UI** to review and improve your Claude context:
- Visual graph of context relationships
- Auto-queries to find stale content
- Scheduled review templates
- Tag-based organization
- OneDrive sync across computers

**Backend:** Links to `C:\Users\emarquez\.claude\` (where Claude reads context from)

